<span id="freeTextContainer11627683853708011063">You can always tell just how great a book is by how sad you are to finish reading it. I was VERY sad to finish Come Find Me. I was torn the entire book between wanting to finish it so I could see how the story ended and not ever wanting it to end. The author painted a very vivid picture throughout the book. It was very easy to imagine each scene and all of the characters. I hope the author releases a new book soon!! I highly recommend Come Find Me!! </span>

          </span>
